  USER INPUT
      в†“
  в”Њв”Ђв†’ [A] ROUTING & CLASSIFICATION (router.py)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Intent Detection
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Keywords: greetings в†’ CHAT
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Keywords: file, search, run в†’ TOOL
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Keywords: explain, how в†’ STRUCTURED
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Keywords: analyze, complex в†’ REASONING
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Patterns: code blocks в†’ RECALL
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Lane Selection
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Lane.RECALL (retrieve past solutions)
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Lane.STANDARD (general conversation)
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Lane.STRUCTURED (explanations)
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Lane.REASONING (complex analysis)
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Lane.TOOL_USE (execute tools)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Confidence Score (0.0-1.0)
  в”‚       в””в”Ђв†’ Determines if override needed
  в”‚
  в”њв”Ђв†’ [B] COMPLEXITY ANALYSIS (complexity_analyzer.py)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Calculate Complexity Score
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Length penalty (long = complex)
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Nesting detection (brackets, indents)
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Technical term count
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Reference complexity (@, imports)
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Output: 0.0-1.0 score
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Recommend Resources
  в”‚       в”њв”Ђв†’ 0.0-0.3 в†’ 25% (MINIMAL)
  в”‚       в”њв”Ђв†’ 0.3-0.5 в†’ 40% (LOW)
  в”‚       в”њв”Ђв†’ 0.5-0.7 в†’ 55% (MODERATE)
  в”‚       в””в”Ђв†’ 0.7+ в†’ 75% (AGGRESSIVE)
  в”‚
  в”њв”Ђв†’ [C] RESOURCE ALLOCATION (runtime_profiles.py + conversation_state.py)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Get Conversation Floor
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Track: turn_count, tool_calls, peak_complexity
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Floor increases gradually (never decreases!)
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ After 3 turns: min 35%, 5 turns: 40%, etc.
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Get Context Minimum
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ <100 words в†’ 25%
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ 100-200 в†’ 35%
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ 200-400 в†’ 50%
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ 400-600 в†’ 60%
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ >1000 в†’ 65%
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Combine: max(complexity, floor, context)
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ CRITICAL: Never decrease resources mid-session
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Tool Boost (if TOOL_USE lane)
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Force minimum 75% for tool operations
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Apply Resource Profile
  в”‚       в”њв”Ђв†’ 25% MINIMAL: 3072 ctx, 1 thread
  в”‚       в”њв”Ђв†’ 50% LOW: 5120 ctx, 2 threads
  в”‚       в”њв”Ђв†’ 60% MODERATE: 6554 ctx, 3 threads
  в”‚       в””в”Ђв†’ 75% AGGRESSIVE: 8192 ctx, 4+ threads
  в”‚
  в””в”Ђв†’ [D] CONTEXT BUILDING (ConversationHistory.get_context())
      в”‚
      в”њв”Ђв†’ Load Last 5 Conversation Entries
      в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Include: user_input
      в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Include: tool_calls results
      в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Format: "вњ“ tool_name: output (150 char max)"
      в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Exclude: full assistant responses (avoid bias)
      в”‚
      в”њв”Ђв†’ Add Session Summary (if available)
      в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Compressed bullets of recent topics
      в”‚
      в””в”Ђв†’ Build Context String
          в””в”Ђв†’ Output: "User: X\n[Tool results: ...]\nUser: Y"


  в•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ
