                    PRIORITY 2: TOOL ORCHESTRATION (if needed)
  в•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ
  в•ђв•ђ

  в”Њв”Ђв†’ [E] TOOL CALL DETECTION (format_translator.py)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Parse Model Response
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Detect JSON: {"type":"tool_call",...}
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Detect Python: tool_name(args)
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Detect Gemma: <tool_call>{...}</tool_call>
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Normalize to standard format
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Extract Tool Name + Args
  в”‚       в””в”Ђв†’ Pass to validation
  в”‚
  в”њв”Ђв†’ [F] SCHEMA VALIDATION (tool_schema_validator.py)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Check Tool Exists
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ If unknown: warn but allow (permissive mode)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Validate Parameters
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Required params present?
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Case-insensitive matching
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Fuzzy match for typos (difflib)
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Filter hallucinated params
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Track Rejections
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Save to logs/validation/parameter_rejections.json
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Return: (is_valid, warnings, filtered_args)
  в”‚       в””в”Ђв†’ Always execute (even with warnings)
  в”‚
  в”њв”Ђв†’ [G] ORCHESTRATOR VALIDATION (tool_orchestrator.py)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Check Tool Availability
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ In ToolManager.get_available_tools()?
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Assess Risk Level
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ SAFE: file_read, grep_search
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ MEDIUM: file_write, file_edit
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ HIGH: file_delete, bash_execute
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ CRITICAL: destructive operations
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Request Confirmation (if needed)
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ confirmation_gate() for MEDIUM+ risk
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Build ToolOperation
  в”‚       в””в”Ђв†’ {tool_name, operation, parameters, risk}
  в”‚
  в”њв”Ђв†’ [H] TOOL EXECUTION (tools.py via ToolManager)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Execute Tool
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Call: tool.execute(**parameters)
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Monitor: resource usage
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Timeout: per tool settings
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Capture: output, errors
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Format Result
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ file_search: Add "Found X files" summary
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ file_read: Add line/char count
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ bash_execute: Add exit code
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ All: Add next_action_hint
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Return ToolResult
  в”‚       в””в”Ђв†’ {success, output, error, metadata}
  в”‚
  в”њв”Ђв†’ [I] AUTO-CHAINING (if applicable)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Detect Safe Chain
  в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ file_search в†’ file_read (if 1 result)
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ directory_list в†’ file_read (if 1 file)
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в”њв”Ђв†’ Execute Follow-up Automatically
  в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Saves 1 model call!
  в”‚   в”‚
  в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ Combine Results
  в”‚       в””в”Ђв†’ Return both: search result + file contents
  в”‚
  в””в”Ђв†’ [J] TOOL RESULT STORAGE
      в”‚
      в”њв”Ђв†’ Add to ConversationEntry.tool_calls
      в”‚   в””в”Ђв†’ [{tool, parameters, success, output, error}]
      в”‚
      в””в”Ђв†’ Format for Model
          в””в”Ђв†’ Pass combined results to next step


